---
title: Double Honey-Soy Beef Steak & Green Veggies with Chilli & Coriander
description: Sweet, savoury, and sizzling with flavour, this honey-soy steak is a weeknight winner! Juicy, caramelised beef meets a vibrant mix of crisp greens, all tossed in a glossy, umami-packed sauce. A hit of fresh chilli and coriander brings just the right amount of zing!

